title: chore(deps): Bump embarkstudios/cargo-deny-action action to v2, bytemuck (yanked)
chore: Bump iai-callgrind, rstest, fix clippy warnings ...
body:
This pr fixes:

* Caching in the ci disabled for miri jobs and fix caching in benchmarks job
* Bump rstest -> 0.18.1 (locked) and in Cargo.toml to latest
* Bump iai-callgrind -> 0.13.3
* Fix clippy warnings and formatting issues
* Update deny configuration file to latest format
* Fix benchmarks job to use `binstall --no-confirm`
* Bump transitive dev-dependency `ahash`
